{"tid":572380,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺好多蝗都有禮貌過香港人","createTime":"2018-02-25T13:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T18:00:38.000Z","uid":150881,"like":112,"dislike":140,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"190fabc86c8e954ea3cf0b0d40b1352179e03eac","tid":572380,"uid":150881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:48:39.000Z","msg":"我喺某大百貨嘅part time sales<br />\n日日見盡唔同嘅客人<br />\n<br />\n但蝗同香港人真係好大差別<br />\n蝗每次買完野或者問野都會唔該前唔該後<br />\n<br />\n但香港人做每樣野都唔會講唔該<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅貨喺pat咗一盒一盒 用膠紙痴住<br />\n但香港人竟然問都唔問就自己開咗個盒攞個貨出嚟睇<br />\n咁冇教養都有<br />\n<br />\n而蝗就會問咗我地先開 就算趕時間都會等<br />\n<br />\n我唔喺想講蝗高質素啲 而係想講香港人幾時變成咁 <br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人有同感？"},{"pid":"4083b17eb061204c2acd85667ccc2265216805ae","tid":572380,"uid":20867,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:49:39.000Z","msg":"新香港人"},{"pid":"fa7181ae94ba43eb20c4bfdba69660e41f4083f4","tid":572380,"uid":150881,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"4083b17eb061204c2acd85667ccc2265216805ae","tid":572380,"uid":20867,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:49:39.000Z","msg":"新香港人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:50:54.000Z","msg":"真心做咗一排先有感而發 我覺得對住蝗客仲想對住香港人 唉點解會咁"},{"pid":"cfc1103c5f991a039997c9616d72c52e42f60f86","tid":572380,"uid":167780,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"聽好多行業都講 香港人最撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796b393e68e234596b0ab7d669dc437bc16c1312","tid":572380,"uid":11245,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:54:11.000Z","msg":"中年嗰班一定係"},{"pid":"007b711fc15efc4a4ab8215bf340e38b815377d2","tid":572380,"uid":150881,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfc1103c5f991a039997c9616d72c52e42f60f86","tid":572380,"uid":167780,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"聽好多行業都講 香港人最撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=